snippet: Leaders Chelsea tightened their stranglehold on the Premier League after a 1-0 win at Crystal Palace earned them an 11th consecutive victory and sent them nine points clear on Saturday....
lead_paragraph: Leaders Chelsea tightened their stranglehold on the Premier League after a 1-0 win at Crystal Palace earned them an 11th consecutive victory and sent them nine points clear on Saturday.

headline.main: Eleven in a Row Chelsea Are Kings of the Palace
headline.print_headline: Eleven in a Row Chelsea Are Kings of the Palace
